{"tid":2472712,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇人講就等我講】連仔！你知道我地有大客光臨嗎？【引入英文介面】","createTime":"2021-04-02T15:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:15:52.000Z","uid":177719,"like":115,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9d438cf4524f7934b9e6d665427d91c02fcbd9f0","tid":2472712,"uid":177719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連仔！你知道我地有大客光臨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n佢就係成人台人氣作家CP個泰國老婆Monmon<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMonmon為咗mon住佢老公，同埋好似話欣賞連鼠夠可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，24個鐘前開咗個ac，大駕光臨成人台CP ching個po*。CP嫂大人有大量，唔bin老公c之餘，仲平易近人到肯係聽完我宣傳之後入咗黎蝦乾po^玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然Monmon嘅中文閱讀程度就只有理解單詞左右，但佢都好努力融入我哋，用Google Translate加英文同我地溝通。Monmon同我地提到佢喺香港冇乜朋友，好開心我地作為連登清泉咁歡迎佢入嚟玩。咁我就覺得既然人地都開咗ac，又入鄉隨俗黎同我地交流，冇理由淨係入嚟上述兩個post玩架嘛。但係連登除咗World台之外，一概都中文黎嘅，趕客咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/there.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n所以小妹就有個提議，未必話要第一步就每個台都增設英文翻譯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；我地可以循序漸進，整個英文介面嚟嘆吓先好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？At least引用、預覽、發送、不推文、會員加密之類都整返個英文版，等我哋嘅外國朋友可以容易啲上手學識呢啲簡單功能，咁要融入都容易啲吖！你話係咪呢連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n而家個勢就係社交移民，主張破舊立新，摒棄Facebook/instagram/twitter/whatsapp等舊霸主壟斷嘅局面。連Trumptrump都要研發新嘅社交媒體，點解連仔唔考慮吓加強自己本身嘅競爭力呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/short.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n連登於香港之人氣，由會員數量之多與開po者質素之高可見一斑。而放眼國際，又有邊條戰線可以好似連字頭咁有號召力，輕易動員有識之士，左右社會輿論風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？既然如此，汝何不先磨利刀，後帶此上佳之器衝出香港，邁向國際呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n為咗逐漸邁向國際，相信連仔你明白引入英文介面嘅重要性。要講嘅嘢係咁多，得閒入嚟蝦乾po玩吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林夏Maid字<br />\n會員編號#177719<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>延伸閱讀</em></strong><br />\n* 補習補到食埋人妻: 後編(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2443114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2443114</a><br />\n<br />\n^ [Alicehaha]虐兒成癮成為虐兒界KOL嘅滙豐職員馬丁林之妻名蝦乾-AKA怨婦界林鄭、廁所打卡KOL(68)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2469067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2469067</a>"},{"pid":"6892584a79868013902df1d6b3fc1949ab939243","tid":2472712,"uid":124330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"幫推 求連仔睇到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da61c26e9264b4fe92ceabc8c4fb094691eea50","tid":2472712,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"平時手機PS4 switch 都係用英文interface <br />\n得連登用中文好kam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed152bc5b1ebbe6d75c722895b7261192c3bcaa","tid":2472712,"uid":177719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6892584a79868013902df1d6b3fc1949ab939243","tid":2472712,"uid":124330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"幫推 求連仔睇到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d374013a327239093601d28c86fa9060732884a9","tid":2472712,"uid":177719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1da61c26e9264b4fe92ceabc8c4fb094691eea50","tid":2472712,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"平時手機PS4 switch 都係用英文interface <br />\n得連登用中文好kam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi